            <title>[SPARK-15360] Should print spark-submit usage when no arguments is specified</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-15360</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In spark 1.6.1, it would print spark-submit usage when calling bin/spark-submit without any argument, but in spark 2.0, it would just print error, it would be nice to make it consistent with spark 1.6.1&lt;/p&gt;

